---
import SEO from '../components/SEO.astro';
import TermsLayout from '@/layouts/TermsLayout.astro';

const title = 'Privacy-Policy';
const description = "Privacy and Policy";
---
<TermsLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <SEO title={title} description={description} />
  <section class="hero" id="articles">
    <header>
        <h1>
          Privacy and Policy
        </h1>
        <p>
          Last updated: November 10, 2025
        </p>
      </header>

      <section>
        <p>
          Welcome to LearnCode.live! We care about your privacy, and this policy
          breaks down how we collect, use, and protect your information when you
          use our site (
          <a
            href="https://www.learncode.live"
          >
            https://www.learncode.live
          </a>
          ). For any concerns, reach us at{" "}
          <a
            href="mailto:contact@learncode.live"
          >
            contact@learncode.live
          </a>
          .
        </p>
        <p>
          We’re considered a <strong>“Data Controller”</strong> under the laws
          of India.
        </p>

        <h3>What We Collect</h3>
        <p>
          We may collect: Full Name, Email, Cookies, Phone, Location, Payment
          Info (via third-party processors), and Browsing Activity. Most of this
          is provided directly by you - when signing up, submitting forms, or
          using our services.
        </p>

        <h3>How We Use Your Info</h3>
        <p>We collect data through:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Google Analytics</li>
          <li>Cookies</li>
          <li>Registration & Contact Forms</li>
          <li>Account Creation</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We use your data for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Account Setup (Full Name, Email, Phone)</li>
          <li>Communication (Email, Phone)</li>
          <li>Analytics & Personalization (Location)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We process your data based on <strong>consent</strong>.
        </p>

        <h3>Who We Share It With</h3>
        <p>
          We may share data with trusted partners like Google Analytics to
          improve services and performance. This includes Advertising and
          Analytics tools.
        </p>

        <h3>Google AdSense and DoubleClick Cookie</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Google, as a third-party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads on LearnCode.live.</li>
          <li>Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to our users based on their visit to our site and/or other sites on the Internet.</li>
          <li>Users may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://adssettings.google.com">Google Ads Settings</a>.</li>
          <li>Alternatively, users can opt out of a third-party vendor's use of cookies for personalized advertising by visiting <a href="www.aboutads.info">www.aboutads.info</a>.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Cookies & Tracking</h3>
        <p>We use cookies for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Analytics</li>
          <li>Advertising</li>
          <li>Functional preferences</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You’ll see a banner asking for your consent when you visit.</p>

        <h3>Your Rights</h3>
        <p>Under data protection laws (like GDPR), you have rights to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access your data</li>
          <li>Rectify inaccuracies</li>
          <li>Request erasure</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To exercise these rights, contact us or use your account settings.
          We’ll respond within 30 days and may verify your identity for
          security.
        </p>

        <h3>California Residents</h3>
        <p>We disclose what data we collect and why before collecting it.</p>

        <h3>Kids’ Privacy</h3>
        <p>
          We do not target children under 13 and do not knowingly collect their
          data. If we discover such data, we’ll delete it immediately.
        </p>

        <h3>Changes to This Policy</h3>
        <p>
          We may update this policy periodically. Major changes will be
          announced via on-site notices.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Last updated:</strong> 2025-11-10
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Effective from:</strong> 2025-11-10
        </p>

        <h3>Embedded Content</h3>
        <p>
          We may embed content from platforms like YouTube, Facebook, Twitter,
          or Google Maps. These platforms may collect data independently.
        </p>

        <h3>Need Help?</h3>
        <p>
          For privacy-related questions, contact us at{" "}
          <a
            href="mailto:contact@learncode.live"
          >
            contact@learncode.live
          </a>
          .
        </p>
      </section>
  </section>
</TermsLayout>
